{"tid":1481980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家唔好再捉鬼","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:03:46.000Z","uid":172981,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"15ff4a1196ca45ef21d288b156a88e1d6fccce67","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱用標題黨開post對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼就咪係五年前輸嘅其中一個原因囉</span></span></strong><br />\n過咗成兩個幾月嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山</strong></span><br />\n點解又突然倒退返五年前㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咗和理非勇武缺一不可<br />\n勇武都係想保護一班和理非<br />\n點解依家揸住支行山仗又話係鬼<br />\n用60926又話係鬼<br />\nSet防線又話係鬼<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位可唔可以相信返前線嘅行動同判斷能力</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以再輸啦<br />\n唔係要大家停止捉鬼<br />\n而係唔好將主線變成捉鬼<br />\n咁樣只會令大家越嚟越分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家都係坐埋同一條船<br />\n無得割㗎，一割就沉船</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n因果由國 容港治己<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"37f72f9dd9892857ff2537dffe18aabdd3185d60","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e40c6e6d4d378789e92563e7ea5fd1b917af617","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b10b3505cdd487d4a0a17c7093ee79880c212fc2","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510344cbf960b7c6e13b129a979b29096f276cce","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a7550fed828d020b2b658746d8d8d116d2d4e","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23f0dbc5d1318c78c540c26987e903bba82c7562","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"唔好重蹈覆轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0635c234c9f44a2d3483cdd628687d3376c451","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96f7d627b5e24d3f0b5f3595753a8d1be3fd9377","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfecdc81fe060d1fb09ab2f30d0f8d0951f1228e","tid":1481980,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"7a67463e85172c5150f99eec89d586f685d0e4a7","tid":1481980,"uid":172981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfecdc81fe060d1fb09ab2f30d0f8d0951f1228e","tid":1481980,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cda4f250ce6e5cffab3467d1067127af3bd5db","tid":1481980,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔捉<br />\n但要提醒，必要時阻止"},{"pid":"ef303dd740194841249d04ee81f37e992b977536","tid":1481980,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0ba08659c09b748cb3923486079545d49fcf131","tid":1481980,"uid":60129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"set防線唔係咁都鬼吓哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nset咋wo<br />\n你唔好話我帶個頭盔就係想殺差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487af4953d9bdcc464d348d444c5492bfa843bcd","tid":1481980,"uid":255473,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0f7519f9688c7426d4a9ac4739c2f56afc8691f","tid":1481980,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"f576c2ce7125c875cabad463d237de3ce5abe791","tid":1481980,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"130a17eb903414353751cb5248440e551a84915b","tid":1481980,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:49:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係捉鬼既時候<br />\n一個不能少<br />\n818 維園見</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ac1df81edab3572e603c6352e511d84ed6864d0c","tid":1481980,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"與其捉鬼，不如自己保持冷靜同理智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c77cf3b8f609159d4adfb38395a62ad898e5e9","tid":1481980,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"見到粉紅豬咀就話人係鬼，呢個太誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家唔洗特意捉鬼<br />\n時刻保持獨立分析能力：<br />\n－有人叫你去圍，諗清楚圍既地方同今日主題有否違逆？<br />\n－有人叫散水，諗清楚今日目標達成未？<br />\n－如果呼籲既行動係從來都未做過，諗清楚會否非常危險？<br />\n－香港人已經係命運共同體，每個人每一步都可以影響國際聲譽，左右外國對香港既態度，任何行動都必需謹慎<br />\n<br />\n真係遇到鬼就要：<br />\n－保持冷靜，企開一邊，影相做證<br />\n－真係捉到人，喺塊鬼臉寫句「平反六四」，影相放人<br />\n－記住大家都可能會認錯人做鬼，凡事不需去太盡，殺鬼都於事無補<br />\n<br />\n維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0535c21f940ad837f11f5f8af970a8d62a401a72","tid":1481980,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487af4953d9bdcc464d348d444c5492bfa843bcd","tid":1481980,"uid":255473,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"c21af3b994229561a5f51dd395197549849dd182","tid":1481980,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"死黑警"}]}